，流程的简化，风险的规避。我认为经验的有用之处在于它的应用。或许对于国内的主流商业模式来说，是这样的。 之所以会产生矛盾，也是在我看过公司的产品之后，感觉所谓的经验并没有帮助项目进行创造，只是不断的复刻自己或别人的已有内容。这方面，我没看到经验起到的积极作用。"},"attached_info":"Cj4IsY3pj9ikiLJwEAMaCDc0Mjc0MTMxIM79tI0GMAA4aUAkcgk1MDM5Njg5Mzh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-29432febe248518968fbf4fbb82d9529_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"37_1643509392.6940863","card_id":"Q_512412683","target":{"id":512412683,"title":"大学生打唇钉会影响找工作吗？很想打怎么办？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/512412683","type":"question","created":1642608170,"answer_count":397,"follower_count":519,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[523,1746,6603,35423,1322452],"comment_count":68,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"大一学生，很想打唇钉，但身边好多人劝不要打，打了会有什么影响呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IsY3pj9ikiLJwEAMaCDc2MTUxMTA2IKrsoI8GMEQ4hwRAJXIJNTEyNDEyNjgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"38_1643509392.6944013","card_id":"Q_513850882","target":{"id":513850882,"title":"郝杰导演的短篇《桔子》你有什么看法?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/513850882","type":"question","created":1643371536,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":63,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2805,26975],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IsY3pj9ikiLJwEAMaCDc2NDcwNjE0IJC4z48GMAA4P0Amcgk1MTM4NTA4ODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1643509392.6946747","card_id":"Q_407479441","target":{"